 />\n<br />\n用法：食肉喝湯。<br />\n<br />\n功效：滋陰涼血，益氣潤膚，解毒祛熱"},{"pid":"e515d150e6fbcfc02dbb34866b0552189577c710","tid":1725084,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a87cc24a5d56020b28198f6da459b535c9c1c8c3","tid":1725084,"uid":91833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca59edb19a63feb8beea747d8616c66245d629d2","tid":1725084,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:49:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AyUYeLrXqug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAyUYeLrXqug&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BNB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=19609593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AyUYeLrXqug</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:38:20.000Z","msg":"Flemish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0765fd0362559f5f3563a6905c91dbbb890de4ee","tid":1725084,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:11:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">領養了兔子,瘋狂跳兔子舞!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n跳兔子舞(Binky)是兔子最開心的狀態。這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Mu27kYckovg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMu27kYckovg&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BNB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=dd5e9852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Mu27kYckovg</a>"},{"pid":"e034fa02908f918e3c0d187a067afe54a15c4ca2","tid":1725084,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:47:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">狗狗搶嘢食, 兔兔毫無還擊之力 !</span></span><br />\n<br />\n兔子側面看某東西代表正面看某東西，你在牠後面也會看到你。(你可想像正前方是盲點，看得最清楚，前腳移動有限，又怎會攻擊到他人？）😭😆🙈:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JKwW65LcLIg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJKwW65LcLIg&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BNB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=cab8df26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JKwW65LcLIg</a>"},{"pid":"70b8b3d6e7736312d0ab4f0202a8d50945066741","tid":1725084,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T23:46:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子生日Party !!</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NfkeOcEHtOk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNfkeOcEHtOk&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BNB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=be7e0b6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NfkeOcEHtOk</a>"},{"pid":"48107d92f05b52ed1362375a35d81b42a13400e3","tid":1725084,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T02:37:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子會不會叫? 是會的....</span></span><br />\n<br />\n開心時會「<span style=\"color: red;\">屋屋</span>」聲叫：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mPoSiZmzo58\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmPoSiZmzo58&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BNB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=9eb9f5c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mPoSiZmzo58</a><br />\n<br />\n不滿時會<span style=\"color: red;\">咕咕叫</span>。後腳大力踏地代表不滿，但也可以代表驚慌覺得有危險，要看當時的情況。在大自然內，兔子後腳大力踏地是用來警告其他兔仔(包括你)有危險。當兔子遇到巨大驚慌或痛苦也會尖叫，例如被捕獵者(predator)追殺和吃的時候，當然這情況是很慘。<br />\n<br />\n以下video 可看到<span style=\"color: red;\">咕咕叫</span>。當牠用鼻碰主人的手然後縮低代表想被撫摸:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Z8wfR7k3844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZ8wfR7k3844&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BNB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=f2cf50eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Z8wfR7k3844</a>"},{"pid":"11cc9599821c7b93b65adfbd6df814197c363a30","tid":1725084,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T04:16:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子開心到極!&nbsp;🌟🐰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n跳兔子舞(Binky)是兔子最開心的狀態。這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活。兔子也會舒適地躺在地上，伸展手腳，還會打翻騰。室內飼養會比室外養長命，因為沒有天氣和敵人威脅，感到安全、平靜和舒適。狗吠聲、雷暴、消防車叫聲等也會嚇驚兔子。當牠們受驚時，也需要groom(撫摸/親吻)牠們，令牠們冷靜下來知道是沒事的。我家的兔子一聽到吸塵機聲音就嚇驚，所以每次我工人吸塵的時候，我會一直撫摸他們，幾次後他們已習慣了 !<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpqOeRBSpaCs&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BNB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=2c977a0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DE90ikFGQTqs&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BNB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=d119548b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs</a>"},{"pid":"ee9aa13dcbb63d49ae6bf3896665a5c83d81330d","tid":1725084,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:06:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子吃西瓜</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由於糖份高，這video分咗幾日比兔仔食。糖份高不宜多吃，否則損害腸胃，患上致命的GI stasis!<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SXw7zGeWMhU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSXw7zGeWMhU&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BNB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=d565fae5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SXw7zGeWMhU</a>"}]}